---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Blog | RealityFoundation" active="blog">
  <div class="pb-8 border-b mb-10" style="border-color: var(--color-line);">
    <p class="mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest" style="color: var(--color-muted);">Blog</p>
    <h1>Notes & Commentary</h1>
    <p>
      Shorter-form writing from the team: research notes, commentary on
      developments in synthetic media, and thinking-in-progress that does not
      yet meet the bar for a formal publication.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Categories -->
  <div
    style="display:flex; gap:var(--space-2); flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:var(--space-8);"
  >
    <span class="tag" style="cursor:default;">Research notes</span>
    <span class="tag" style="cursor:default;">Policy commentary</span>
    <span class="tag" style="cursor:default;">Event reports</span>
    <span class="tag" style="cursor:default;">Field observations</span>
  </div>

  <!-- Empty state -->
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center py-20 px-8 border-2 border-dashed rounded-lg" style="color: var(--color-muted); border-color: var(--color-line);">
    <div style="font-size:2rem; margin-bottom:var(--space-4); opacity:0.4;">
      &#9632;
    </div>
    <h3>First post coming soon</h3>
    <p>
      We are preparing our first set of posts. Topics will include synthetic
      media trends, notes from the research programme, and commentary on
      relevant policy developments.
    </p>
    <a href="/get-involved" class="btn btn-primary">Get notified</a>
  </div>

  <!-- What to expect -->
  <section class="mb-16" style="margin-top:var(--space-16);">
    <div class="mb-8">
      <h2>What you will find here</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid gap-4" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(min(280px, 100%), 1fr));">
      <div class="card">
        <p class="card-eyebrow">Research notes</p>
        <h3>Behind the work</h3>
        <p>
          Informal notes on what we are reading, methodological decisions we are
          wrestling with, and early results that are not yet ready for formal
          publication.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <p class="card-eyebrow">Policy commentary</p>
        <h3>Developments we are watching</h3>
        <p>
          Brief analysis of AI Act provisions, court decisions on digital
          evidence, and regulatory movements relevant to synthetic media
          detection.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <p class="card-eyebrow">Field observations</p>
        <h3>Cases in the wild</h3>
        <p>
          When a notable deepfake, manipulation, or provenance failure makes the
          news, we will write about what it means technically and what it
          reveals about the problem.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
